Are you asked to repeat yourself?

Do you feel self-conscious about how you sound?

Is your accent holding you back professionally or socially?

Language East provides accent modification therapy to improve our clients’ communication skills. Accent modification is direct instruction and practice aimed at improving the clarity and understandability of a client’s spoken language.

We offer individual and group classes. In order to learn more information go to our website languageeast.com or contact us at languageeast@gmail.com.
